Earth + Water = Plant
Plant + Wind = Dandelion

Dandelion + Water = Wine
Water + Wine = Holy Water
Holy Water + Tree = Jesus
Jesus + Tree = Cross  // 7



Gen 1 - 40 Elements -> 40 Total Elements
Gen 2 - 128 Elements -> 168 Total Elements
Gen 3 - 392 Elements -> 560 Total Elements
Gen 4 - 1057 Elements -> 1617 Total Elements
Gen 5 - 2993 Elements -> 4610 Total Elements
